These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, journalist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, rock
There are 2 different nationalities: french, malaysian
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goat
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, yellow
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
4. the french is on the right of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk       | mirinda    |
| Job           | journalist | accountant |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | folk   |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | french     |
| Pet           | goat       | ferret     |
| Color     | ivory     | yellow        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
2 different games are played: whist, chess
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
House: cape-cod, ranch-style
2 different pets are kept: bird, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person drinking water is the ranch-style house##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up        | water   |
| Game         | chess | whist |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| House   | cape-cod       | ranch-style     |
| Pet           | rat        | bird    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, pepper
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daisy
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile
1. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | pepper    | avocado      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | colombian    |
| Flower           | sunflower       | daisy   |
| Transport         | snowmobile   | airplane     |

