3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the modern house##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Beverage      | coffee    | sprite      |
| House          | modern | ranch-style |
| Movie-Genre           | animation     | documentary      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       |
